                    <span>I have read every book on the subject matter.
<br />
<br />There has never been a book of substance written on online no limit tournament poker.  I thought this would be the one.  Harrington imparts a few decent points but fills over half the book with "problems", making it completely unreadable.
<br />
<br />If online no limit holdem tourneys are your thing, the book is worth a read - just don't expect too much from it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best Tourney Book on the Market</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
